: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bel&eacute;m, conhecida como \"Paris Tropical\" e \"Francesinha do Norte\", oferece uma rica infraestrutura tur&iacute;stica, com atra&ccedil;&otilde;es hist&oacute;ricas como o Teatro da Paz, Museu de Arte Sacra e Ver-o-Peso. A cidade tamb&eacute;m &eacute; palco de grandes eventos culturais e religiosos, como a Feira Pan-amaz&ocirc;nica do Livro e a FITA &ndash; Feira Internacional de Turismo da Amaz&ocirc;nia </span></span><span class=\"whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"border: 0px solid #e5e7eb;\"><a class=\"mr-[2px] citation ml-xs inline\" style=\"border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; text-decoration-line: none; margin-left: 4px; margin-right: 2px;\" href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bel%C3%A9m_(Par%C3%A1)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"relative select-none align-middle undefined -top-px default font-sans text-base text-textMain dark:text-textMainDark selection:bg-super/50 selection:text-textMain dark:selection:bg-superDuper/10 dark:selection:text-superDark\" style=\"border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem;\"><span class=\"hover:bg-super dark:hover:bg-superDark dark:hover:text-backgroundDark min-w-[1rem] rounded-[0.3125rem] px-[0.3rem] text-center align-middle font-mono text-[0.6rem] tabular-nums hover:text-white py-[0.1875rem] border-borderMain/50 ring-borderMain/50 divide-borderMain/50 dark:divide-borderMainDark/50 dark:ring-borderMainDark/50 dark:border-borderMainDark/50 bg-offsetPlus dark:bg-offsetPlusDark\" style=\"border: 0px solid; min-width: 1rem; padding: 0.1875rem 0.3rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-family: berkeleyMono, \'berkeleyMono Fallback\', \'ui-monospace\', \'SFMono-Regular\', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">5</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> .</