l;&atilde;o de vulnerabilidade</span></span></strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> .</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Essa &eacute; uma oportunidade de ajudar de forma concreta, enquanto compartilha uma refei&ccedil;&atilde;o com prop&oacute;sito.</span></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">💖 100% da renda destinada ser&aacute; a:</span></span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Melhorias na infraestrutura da sede do Instituto</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Garantia de alimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o para crian&ccedil;as atendidas</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Compra de materiais para oficinas de arte, m&uacute;sica, dan&ccedil;a, esportes e refor&ccedil;o escolar</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O evento &eacute; realizado com o apoio da comunidade e volunt&aacute;rios comprometidos com a transforma&ccedil;&atilde;o social e espiritual de vidas.</span></span></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">📅 </span></span><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Data:</span></span></strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 17 de maio (sexta-feira) </span></span><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">🕕 </span></span><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Hor&aacute;rio:</span></span></strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> A partir das 18h </span></span><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">📍 </span></span><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Local:</span></span></strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Rua Marqu&ecirc;s de Olinda, 2.100 &ndash; S&atilde;o Jos&eacute;/SC</span></span></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Venha saborear uma feijoada deliciosa, encontrar pessoas queridas e fazer parte de algo maior.</span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Com um prato, voc&ecirc; ajuda a alimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o s&oacute; o corpo, mas tamb&eacute;m a esperan&ccedil;a de centenas de crian&ccedil;as.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Contamos com voc&ecirc;!</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"isolate z-3 w-full basis-auto has-data-has-thread-error:pt-2 has-data-has-thread-error:[box-shadow:var(--sharp-edge-bottom-shadow)] md:border-transparent md:pt-0 dark:border-white/20 md:dark:border-transparent flex flex-col\">\r\n<div class=\"text-base mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)\">\r\n<div class=\"[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6\">\r\n<div class=\"relative z-1 flex max-w-full 