<a class=\"mr-[2px] citation ml-xs inline\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;text-decoration-line:none;margin-left:4px;margin-right:2px;\" href=\"https://www.gov.br/turismo/pt-br/assuntos/noticias/cirio-de-nazare-mais-de-400-mil-passageiros-devem-passar-pelo-aeroporto-internacional-de-belem-pa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"relative select-none align-middle undefined -top-px default font-sans text-base text-textMain dark:text-textMainDark selection:bg-super/50 selection:text-textMain dark:selection:bg-superDuper/10 dark:selection:text-superDark\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;vertical-align:middle;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5rem;\"><span class=\"hover:bg-super dark:hover:bg-superDark dark:hover:text-backgroundDark min-w-[1rem] rounded-[0.3125rem] px-[0.3rem] text-center align-middle font-mono text-[0.6rem] tabular-nums hover:text-white py-[0.1875rem] border-borderMain/50 ring-borderMain/50 divide-borderMain/50 dark:divide-borderMainDark/50 dark:ring-borderMainDark/50 dark:border-borderMainDark/50 bg-offsetPlus dark:bg-offsetPlusDark\" style=\"border:0px solid;min-width:1rem;padding:0.1875rem 0.3rem;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-family:berkeleyMono, \'berkeleyMono Fallback\', \'ui-monospace\', \'SFMono-Regular\', monospace;font-size:0.6rem;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\">2</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"> .</span></span></span></p>\n<h2 class=\"mb-xs mt-5 text-base font-[525] first:mt-3\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:1rem;margin:1.25rem 0px 4px;line-height:1.5rem;font-family:fkGrotesk, \'fkGrotesk Fallback\';\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\">Oportunidades para o Turismo Brasileiro Cristão</span></span></h2>\n<p class=\"my-0\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;margin:0px;font-family:fkGroteskNeue, \'fkGroteskNeue Fallback\', \'ui-sans-serif\', \'system-ui\', \'-apple-system\', BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\">A TBC – Turismo Brasileiro Cristão, a maior plataforma do segmento no Brasil, oferece uma excelente oportunidade para promover experiências cristãs durante o Círio de Nazaré. Com foco na hospedagem cristã com propósito, o TBC permite que os membros compartilhem fé, tempo e comunhão, além de promover a vivência e evangelização através de uma rede de hospedagem entre os membros </span></span><span class=\"whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;\"><a class=\"mr-[2px] citation ml-xs inline\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;text-decoration-line:none;margin-left:4px;margin-right:2px;\" href=\"https://repositorio.ufba.br/bitstream/ri/39282/1/1%20Disserta%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20-%20Turismo%20religioso%20-%20final%20-%202.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"relative select-none align-middle undefined -top-px default font-sans text-base text-textMain dark:text-textMainDark selection:bg-super/50 selection:text-textMain dark:selection:bg-superDuper/10 dark:selection:text-superDark\" style=\"border:0px solid #e5e7eb;vertical-align:middle;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5rem;\"><span class=\"hover:bg-super dark:hover:bg-superDark dark:hover:text-backgroundDark min-w-[1rem] rounded-[0.3125rem] px-[0.3rem] text-center align-middle font-mono text-[0.6rem] tabular-nums hover:text-white py-[0.1875rem] border-borderMain/50 ring-borderMain/50 divide-borderMain/50 dark:divide-borderMainDark/50 dark:ring-borderMainDark/50 dark:border-borderMainDark/50 bg-offsetPlus dark:bg-offsetPlusDark\" style=\"border:0px solid;min-width:1rem;padding:0.1875rem 0.3rem;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-family:berkeleyMono, \'berkeleyMono 