(16, 'Tour com Irmão José Carlos – História, Fé e Paisagens de Florianópolis', 'river-cruise-tour-on-the-seine', '<h4><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">📍 </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Roteiro Completo</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> (aprox. 6 a 8h de dura&ccedil;&atilde;o)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ponte Herc&iacute;lio Luz e Catedral Metropolitana</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Iniciamos com uma parada para fotos na emblem&aacute;tica Ponte Herc&iacute;lio Luz, cart&atilde;o-postal da cidade. Logo depois, visitamos a bel&iacute;ssima Catedral no Centro Hist&oacute;rico de Florian&oacute;polis &mdash; um tempo breve de contempla&ccedil;&atilde;o e registros fotogr&aacute;ficos.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Lagoa da Concei&ccedil;&atilde;o &ndash; Mirantes e Igreja Cat&oacute;lica</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Seguimos para a Lagoa da Concei&ccedil;&atilde;o, com paradas nos dois mirantes para fotos e v&iacute;deos incr&iacute;veis. Em seguida, visitamos uma igreja cat&oacute;lica local, momento ideal para orar e apreciar a arquitetura sacra.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Praias da Joaquina e Campeche &ndash; Almo&ccedil;o frente &agrave; Ilha</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Uma jornada continua em dire&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave;s praias da Joaquina e Campeche. Faremos uma pausa para o almo&ccedil;o com vista para a Ilha do Campeche. O card&aacute;pio oferece carne ou peixe, com valor m&eacute;dio de R$ 70 por pessoa (refei&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o inclusa).</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Morro das Pedras &ndash; Mirante do Convento (dispon&iacute;vel)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Ap&oacute;s o almo&ccedil;o, visitamos o Morro das Pedras. Se o mirante do convento estiver aberto, ser&aacute; uma oportunidade especial para tirar fotos e contemplar uma vista deslumbrante.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Arma&ccedil;&atilde;o &ndash; Capela e Trapiche</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Na vila da Arma&ccedil;&atilde;o, visitamos uma encantadora capela local e o trapiche da regi&atilde;o. Um momento de paz e conex&atilde;o com a simplicidade e beleza do lugar.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ribeir&atilde;o da Ilha &ndash; Igreja Hist&oacute;rica e Caf&eacute; &agrave; Beira-Mar</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Encerramos o passeio no bairro mais antigo de Florian&oacute;polis, Ribeir&atilde;o da Ilha. Visitamos uma igreja tradicional e desfrutamos de um caf&eacute; &agrave; beira-mar, cercado pela arquitetura a&ccedil;oriana e pela hist&oacute;ria viva da ilha.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Retorno ao ponto de encontro</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br /><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> Finalizamos o tour retornando ao local combinado, com a alma leve e o cora&ccedil;&atilde;o cheio de boas lembran&ccedil;as.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>', 296, 59, 'From the iconic to the unexpected, the city of San Francisco never ceases to surprise. Kick-start your effortlessly delivered Northern California holiday in the cosmopolitan hills of \'The City\'. Join your Travel Director and fellow travellers for a Welcome Reception at your hotel.Welcome Reception', 4, 11, 'Nevada, US', '36.401066', '-88.312292', 12, 1, '37,38,39,40,41,42,43', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfEiKK-iX70', '220.00', '175.00', 6, 4, 4, '[{\"title\":\"Quem pode participar do passeio?\",\"content\":\"O passeio \\u00e9 aberto a todos! Fam\\u00edlias, jovens, casais, idosos \\u2014 todos s\\u00e3o bem-vindos. A proposta \\u00e9 leve, segura e feita com muito carinho crist\\u00e3o.\"},{\"title\":\"Preciso levar algo espec\\u00edfico?\",\"content\":\"Sugerimos roupas leves, protetor solar, um chap\\u00e9u e cal\\u00e7ado confort\\u00e1vel. E claro, n\\u00e3o esque\\u00e7a sua c\\u00e2mera ou celular para registrar os momentos!\"},{\"title\":\"O almo\\u00e7o est\\u00e1 incluso no valor do passeio?\",\"content\":\"N\\u00e3o. O almo\\u00e7o \\u00e9 feito em restaurante \\u00e0 beira-mar com vista para a Ilha do Campeche, com op\\u00e7\\u00f5es de carne ou peixe. O custo m\\u00e9dio \\u00e9 de R$ 70 por pessoa (pagamento feito no local)\"},{\"title\":\"O passeio tem paradas para ora\\u00e7\\u00e3o ou momentos de f\\u00e9?\",\"content\":\"This tour has an age range of 12-70 years old, this means children under the age of 12 will not be eligible to participate in this tour. However, if you are over 70 years please contact us as you may be eligible to join the tour if you fill out G Adventures self-assessment form.\"},{\"title\":\"E se chover no dia do passeio?\",\"content\":\"Em caso de chuva leve, o passeio segue normalmente, com adapta\\u00e7\\u00f5es se necess\\u00e1rio. Se o clima impedir o trajeto com seguran\\u00e7a, entraremos em contato para remarcar ou oferecer alternativas.\"}]', 'publish', NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-10 23:45:24', '2025-04-18 01:59:44', 1, 1, '2025-10-20 00:00:00', '2025-10-20 00:00:00', '2025-10-19 00:00:00', '[{\"title\":\"Conduzido por crist\\u00e3o local com sensibilidade e cuidado\"},{\"title\":\"Paradas para ora\\u00e7\\u00e3o, contempla\\u00e7\\u00e3o e fotos\"},{\"title\":\"Mistura de cultura, paisagem e f\\u00e9\"},{\"title\":\"Ideal para fam\\u00edlias, grupos crist\\u00e3os e visitantes em retiro\"},{\"title\":\"\\ud83d\\udc55 Recomendado:\"},{\"title\":\"Roupas leves e confort\\u00e1veis\"},{\"title\":\"Protetor solar e chap\\u00e9u\"},{\"title\":\"C\\u00e2mera ou celular carregado\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"\\ud83c\\udf7d\\ufe0f Alimenta\\u00e7\\u00e3o\"},{\"title\":\"Almo\\u00e7o em restaurante com vista para o mar. Valor m\\u00e9dio de R$ 70 (n\\u00e3o incluso\"},{\"title\":\"Cafe com vista para o mar Valor m\\u00e9dio de R$ 30 (n\\u00e3o incluso\"}]', '[{\"image_id\":\"296\",\"title\":\"Dia 1\",\"desc\":\"Florian\\u00f3polis\",\"content\":\"Tour passando por pontos hist\\u00f3ricos e de f\\u00e9: Ponte Herc\\u00edlio Luz, Catedral, mirantes da Lagoa, igrejas locais, praias da Joaquina e Campeche, Morro das Pedras, Arma\\u00e7\\u00e3o e Ribeir\\u00e3o da Ilha. Um dia de paisagens, ora\\u00e7\\u00e3o e comunh\\u00e3o crist\\u00e3.\"}]', '4.5', NULL, 1, '[{\"name\":\"taxa de servi\\u00e7o\",\"desc\":null,\"name_en\":null,\"desc_en\":null,\"price\":\"15\",\"unit\":\"percent\",\"type\":\"one_time\",\"per_person\":\"on\"}]', NULL, 'outubro 20', '12+', 'Rodoviária de Florianópolis', NULL, 1, 2);
